Package: di-utils-shell
Architecture: any
Depends: di-utils
XB-installer-menu-item: 950
Description: Execute a shell
 Use this module to execute an interactive shell within debian-installer.

Package: di-utils-fake-partitioner
Architecture: all
Provides: partitioned-harddrives
Description: I have already partitioned the hard drive
 Use this module if you have already partitioned your hard drive.

Package: di-utils-fake-mkfs
Architecture: all
Depends: partitioned-harddrives
Provides: made-filesystems
Description: I have already created file systems
 Use this module if you have already made file systems on your 
 partitions.

Package: di-utils-fake-mkswap
Architecture: all
Depends: partitioned-harddrives
Provides: made-swapspace
Description: Already made swapspace
 Use this module if you have already made swapspace on your
 partitions.

Package: di-utils-fake-mount-partitions
Architecture: all
Depends: made-filesystems
Provides: mounted-partitions
Description: I have already mounted the partitions
 Use this module if you have already mounted the partitions yourself.

